apps.name: NeoFreeBird

apps.versionDescription:
Twitter, version 10.94:

NeoFreeBird, version 1.0:
Improved various translations in all locales (#13, #15)
Added Croatian and Ukrainian (thanks @ytrav)
[Beta] Added the Tweet source label (like Twitter for iPhone and so on, thanks @nyathea)
Made the Twitter bird follow the accent color (#20, thanks @nyathea)
Added the seasonal Twitter icons from 2022
Added the ability to disable the individual Photos/Videos tabs, the Articles tab, and the Highlights tab on profiles (thanks @nyathea)
Added the ability to disable the compact interaction buttons on Tweets (thanks @nyathea)
Redesigned the NeoFreeBird settings page
Fixed tap-and-hold to speed up videos (#9)
Fixed the Video Download button causing crashes on 10.94 and beyond
